WEBVTT

00:00:31.997 --> 00:00:35.997
Specijalno za forum IPTV Zezanje

00:00:38.997 --> 00:00:40.123
<i>Hej, hej, hej!</i>

00:00:41.083 --> 00:00:42.250
<i>Koji kurac?</i>

00:00:44.044 --> 00:00:45.878
<i>Čekaj! Moram dojaviti!</i>

00:00:48.841 --> 00:00:49.882
<i>Miči se!</i>

00:00:58.892 --> 00:00:59.892
<i>Hej!</i>

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:02.895
<i>Bobby, čuješ me?</i>

00:01:09.695 --> 00:01:11.237
<i>Ma tu, pička ti materina!</i>

00:01:28.380 --> 00:01:29.672
<i>Molim te!</i>

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:31.716
<i>Daj, jebote, stani, čovječe!</i>

00:01:31.884 --> 00:01:33.551
<i>Daj spusti pištolj!</i>

00:01:36.472 --> 00:01:37.638
<i>Ma daj.</i>

00:01:38.849 --> 00:01:39.891
<i>Molim te.</i>

00:01:40.934 --> 00:01:42.477
<i>Jebemu, preklinjem te.</i>

00:01:42.644 --> 00:01:45.188
<i>Nisam ga ni pipnuo!
Nisam ni pipnuo tog starog!</i>

00:01:45.355 --> 00:01:46.481
<i>Nisam čak ni...</i>

